Starscream struggled to his feet. He had been in stasis lock and 
really damaged. His body was so schorched that wires were hanging out 
all over the place. He went to the others.

"Phobia, good to see you're all right. Now.....are we all okay? Good. 
Now, as Emperor of the Decpticons, I order a full fledged assault on 
organic. Watch out for Earth, he hates me. We can win this if we try. 
Jungle Monkey should take the right left, and i'll go up front 
through the backwards!"

Starscream collapsed again.
